headline: ENA Foundation Honors Three with Keystone Award
summary: As part of ENA's annual awards season, the ENA Foundation announced three recipients of the Keystone Award: longtime donor and ENA member Jackie Taylor-Wynkoop; the New Jersey ENA State Council; and corporate partner Stryker.

headline: SYK Q2 Deep Dive: Tariffs, Supply Chain, and Robotics Weigh on Market Sentiment
summary: Medical technology company Stryker (NYSE:SYK) beat Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q2 CY2025, with sales up 11.1% year on year to $6.02 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $3.13 per share was 1.9% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
